This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: top fifty romcom
des: With Valentine’s Day quickly approaching, Rotten Tomatoes has released its ranking of the Top 50 Best Romantic Comedies. These facts features a carefully chosen collection of movies that are guaranteed to make people’s hearts skip a beat. The facts spans decades and includes classics and modern gems, making it the ideal watchlist for anyone looking for a romantic getaway.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
